泉州坍塌事件逃生者独家还原事发经过，建筑改造恐为罪魁。
Quanzhou collapse of the people who escaped the exclusive restoration of the incident, architectural transformation may be the culprit.
毛翊君。
Yijun Mao.
中国新闻周刊                      。
China News Weekly.
中国新闻周刊。
China News Weekly.
