Join me as we move through the fog, seek the truth and keep watch.
。
.
隔离者每天需交200伙食费，逃生后继续被隔离截至3月10日16时38分，从泉州欣佳酒店坍塌事故现场，已救出62人，其中20人遇难，42人受伤，仍有9人被困。
As of 16: 38 a.m. on March 10, 62 people had been rescued from the scene of the collapse of the Xin Jia Hotel in Quanzhou, 20 of whom had been killed, 42 injured and 9 still trapped.
在被隔离者之中，有一人非常幸运地没有受伤，事发之初就与妻子自行逃出。
One of the quarantined was very lucky not to be injured and escaped with his wife at the beginning of the incident.
《中国新闻周刊》联系到这位名为王涛的湖北籍居民，回忆了事故的前前后后。
China News Weekly contacted the Hubei resident, Wang Tao, recalling the circumstances of the accident.
3月7日事发时，王涛和妻子以为地震了，他们逃出来后，看见街上的情形，才明白过来是居住的这栋楼出了事。
March 7 incident, Wang Tao and his wife thought that the earthquake, they fled, see the situation in the street, only to understand that it is living in this building.
王涛跑向临近的小区求助，又返回废墟，拼命喊自己父亲和表弟的名字，但始终没有听到回应。
Wang Tao ran to the neighborhood for help and returned to the ruins, crying desperately for the names of his father and cousin, but never heard a response.
事后他们才得知，自己是最早从坍塌的酒店中自行逃生的两人。
It was only later that they learned that they were the first two to escape from the collapsed hotel.
2月26日，刚从湖北老家来泉州做小生意的王涛一家，被社区安排住进家欣佳酒店进行隔离。
Feb. 26, just from Hubei home to do small business in Quanzhou Wang Tao family, the community arranged to live in the home Xinjia hotel for isolation.
他们住在6层远离街道的一侧，王涛和妻子在612，父亲和表弟分别住在隔壁的616和614。
They live on the 6th floor away from the street, Wang Tao lives with his wife at 612, and their father and cousin live next door at 616 and 614 respectively.
3月7日晚7点左右，夫妻俩刚吃完饭，妻子躺在床上玩手机，王涛坐在床旁的沙发上。
March 7 around 7 p.m., the couple has just finished eating, his wife is lying in bed playing mobile phone, Wang Tao sitting on the sofa beside the bed.
忽然楼下有一声巨响，两三秒之后，天花板剧烈晃动，王涛赶紧去拉妻子，一瞬间房子全部垮下来。
Suddenly there was a loud noise downstairs, two or three seconds later, the ceiling shaking violently, Wang Tao rushed to pull his wife, all the house collapsed in an instant.
王涛的视线里很黑，周围都是灰尘，他感到呼吸有些困难。
Wang Tao's line of sight is very dark, surrounded by dust, he feels a little difficult to breathe.
他喊自己的妻子，得知无碍后，他们努力移动身体。
He called his wife and when they learned it was okay, they tried to move their bodies.
街上的灯光照进来，王涛逐渐看见周围，他们抱住类似钢筋的物体往外爬。
As the street lights came in, Wang Tao gradually saw them crawling out with objects like steel bars in their arms.
爬出废墟后，他们呼喊父亲和表弟，没有应答。
After crawling out of the ruins, they shouted at their father and cousin, did not respond.
他们没有来得及带随身物品，手机也留在了废墟里，只能向周围的社区寻求帮忙。
They did not have time to carry their belongings and their mobile phones were left in ruins, seeking help from the surrounding community.
之后，王涛和妻子又爬进废墟，冲着父亲和表弟房间的方向喊了几分钟，仍然没有任何反应。
After that, Wang Tao and his wife climbed back into the ruins and shouted for a few minutes in the direction of their father's and cousin's room.
此时，高处不断有东西往下掉，他听到楼下的人在呼叫。
At that moment, something kept falling, and he heard people shouting from below.
紧接着，消防人员出现在现场。
Immediately afterwards, firefighters appeared on the scene.
他看见住在自己隔壁房间的一个年轻男子慢慢爬出来。
He saw a young man crawling out of the room next to him.
消防人员循着声音，对王涛楼下和隔壁有呼喊声和动静的住户先采取了救援行动。
The firemen followed the sound and took the first steps to rescue the residents of Wang Tao downstairs and next door who were shouting and shouting.
王涛成为现场唯一没有受伤的当事人，而他的妻子划伤了脚。
Wang Tao became the only uninjured party at the scene and his wife cut her foot.
王涛随医生把妻子送至医院后，又返回现场。
Wang Tao took his wife to hospital with the doctor and returned to the scene.
原本的酒店第六层全部翘起，成了一个斜角，父亲和表弟被深深压进了角落里，他和救援人员一起挖到了8日凌晨两点，发现两人时，已经没有生命迹象。
The original sixth floor of the hotel all turned up, became a diagonal, father and cousin was pushed deep into the corner, he and the rescue workers dug until 2 a.m. on the 8th, when the two found no signs of life.
直到第二天上午9点，房间中的沙发、床、墙体等才被一一移开，救援人员用剪刀剪开了床里的棉絮，才将王涛父亲和表弟的遗体抬了出来。
It was not until 9 a.m. the next morning that the sofa, bed and wall in the room were removed. Rescue workers cut open the cotton wool in the bed with scissors before lifting the bodies of Wang Tao's father and cousin.
“很恐怖。
"It's horrible.
”王涛对《中国新闻周刊》回忆。
Wang Tao recalls China News Weekly.
他现在用的手机，就是父亲的。
The cell phone he's using is his father's.
他说，自己至今吃不下饭。
He said he had not been able to eat.
3月8日下午，王涛把亲人的遗体送到殡仪馆的车上。
On the afternoon of March 8, Wang Tao took the bodies of his relatives to the funeral home.
一位工作人员告知他不能随同过去，因为他本人的隔离期未满。
A staff member informed him that he could not accompany him because his own period of isolation had not expired.
下午5点多，社区的工作人员找到王涛，将其安排到附近的如家酒店，继续隔离。
At 5 p. m., the community workers found Wang Tao and arranged for him to stay in isolation at a nearby hotel like his home.
隔离将在3月11日结束。
The isolation will end on March 11.
朱先生和王涛一家一样，是1月26日被常泰社区安排到欣佳酒店进行隔离的。
Mr. Zhu, like the Wang Tao family, was quarantined at the Xinjia Hotel on January 26 by the Changtai community.
朱先生和妻子孩子被救出，三人伤情不重，只是15岁的儿子牙床被砸伤，已做了手术。
Zhu and his wife and children were rescued, three people were not seriously injured, only 15-year-old son gums were injured, surgery has been done.
他们向《中国新闻周刊》回忆，之前住的8天里都没有感觉到异常。
They told China News Weekly that they had not felt abnormal for eight days.
在欣佳酒店隔离期间，这些住客被要求缴纳每日人均大约200元的食宿费，王涛一家住了8天，陆续交了6000元。
During the isolation period of Xinjia Hotel, the residents were required to pay about 200 yuan per person per day for board and lodging. The Wang Tao family stayed for 8 days and paid 6,000 yuan in succession.
目前，他继续隔离的后续费用还不知道如何处理。
At present, the follow-up costs of his continued isolation are unknown.
欣佳酒店所在的南环路，属于鲤城区常泰上村辖区，靠近鲤城区和泉州县级市南安交界，紧挨着308省道。
Xinjia Hotel is located in the South Ring Road, which belongs to the district of Changtai Sheung Village in Lei City, near the junction of Lei City and Quanzhou County City Nan'an, next to 308 Provincial Road.
七八公里长的沿路，分布着多家品牌汽车店铺，被当地人称作汽车长廊。
Seven or eight kilometers long along the road, there are a number of brands of car shops, known as the local car corridor.
当地人称，40年前，村子闭塞，只有南环路反向一条小土路能够通往泉州市区。
Locals say that 40 years ago the village was isolated and only a small dirt road on the southern ring road led to Quanzhou city.
近年，该村进行了扩建和景观改造，建成现在的沥青路，村里人开始到附近工厂打工。
In recent years, the village underwent expansion and landscape improvement, with the construction of what is now an asphalt road, and villagers began to work in nearby factories.
3月9日至10日，《中国新闻周刊》连续致电泉州市卫健委，希望了解为什么选择将欣佳酒店选做医学隔离观察点，卫健委办公室人员始终称，其主要的工作是医疗救助，定点的事情还有待应急调查组调查之后公布情况。
From 9 to 10 March, China News Weekly continuously called the Quanzhou Health Care Commission to find out why it had chosen to choose Xinjia Hotel as a medical quarantine observation point.
《中国新闻周刊》查询发现，该涉事建筑的详细信息无法在鲤城区住建局官网上查到。
An enquiry by China News Weekly found that details of the building could not be found on the URA website.
《中国新闻周刊》也多次联系鲤城区住建局，该局一位办公室人员回应称，所有信息只能等宣传部统一发布。
A staff member of the bureau of the China News Weekly, which contacted the URA several times, said all the information would have to wait for the Ministry of Publicity to publish it uniformly.
湘广土木工程技术有限公司董事长曾定坤，是建筑工程圈的资深人士，曾在汶川地震后去往汶川参与援建。
Xiangguang Civil Engineering Co. Ltd. Chairman Zeng Dingkun, is a senior figure in the construction industry, Wenchuan after the earthquake to participate in construction assistance.
他向《中国新闻周刊》介绍，在事发之后，他所在的工程圈子曾对这次事故和这家酒店建筑进行过研究，据他的判断，该楼的后期改造可能存在很大的问题。
He told China News that after the incident, his engineering circle had studied the accident and the hotel building, and he judged that the late renovation of the building could be problematic.
他说，最初这栋建筑的每一层的挑高都很高，后来改造时，在整栋建筑高度不变的情况下，又进行隔断增加了使用层数，这就增加了荷载，而且每个套间都有卫生间等设施，这就让荷载变得更重。
Initially, he said, each floor of the building was high in height, and later retrofitted, with the height of the entire building unchanged, it increased the number of floors used, which increased the load, and each suite had facilities such as toilets, which added to the load.
如果这栋建筑是混凝土或者砖混结构，一旦出问题，可能会有一个开裂的过程，在损坏的过程中，内力会重新达到平衡，房子的框架还在，人们逃生的几率就更大，而这栋建筑采用钢结构，稍微超一点就会整体垮掉。
If the building is made of concrete or brick, if something goes wrong, there may be a cracking process in which the internal force is rebalanced, the frame of the house is still in place, and people are more likely to escape, and the structure is steel-framed and collapses slightly above it.
钢结构的优势在于建造周期短，自重比较轻，中间无需立柱的房子会选用钢结构，比如4S店、厂房等等。
The advantage of steel structure is that the construction cycle is short, self-weight is lighter, the middle of the house without column will choose steel structure, such as 4S shop, factory building and so on.
曾定坤说，如果进行楼房的结构改造，涉及到流程审批，首先要跟建筑主管部门报批，之后会颁发一个建筑许可证，然后交图纸，由专业的设计院盖章。
If any structural changes to a building involve process approval, he said, he would first have to seek approval from the construction authorities before issuing a building permit, which would then be handed in the drawings and stamped by the professional design institute.
他说，在酒店行业，尤其是经济型酒店，很多是没有报批的。
'In the hotel industry, especially in budget hotels, a lot of it is not approved, 'he said.
“室内结构属于内装，如果自己不报，负责外观检查的城管部门在后期也不会查到。
"Indoor structure is internal, if they do not report, in charge of the appearance of the inspection of the city management department in the later period will not be found.
”泉州市鲤城区常务副区长黄向阳在3月9日晚介绍，泉州欣佳酒店坍塌事故所有被困人员身份信息全部摸排清楚，并与其家属、亲属取得联系。
Huang Xiangyang, deputy mayor of Quanzhou city's Lei City, said on the night of March 9 that all the people trapped in the collapse of the Quanzhou Xinjia Hotel had been identified and contacted their families and relatives.
在受困的71名人中，男性51人，女性20人，其中湖北籍42人，福建籍14人，浙江籍7人，湖南籍6人、安徽籍1人，重庆籍1人，主要是务工、随行人员、游客。
Of the 71 people stranded, 51 were men and 20 women, including 42 Hubei, 14 Fujian, 7 Zhejiang, 6 Hunan, 1 Anhui and 1 Chongqing, mainly migrant workers, entourage and tourists.
自行逃生的9人，其中福建籍5人、安徽籍1人、黑龙江籍1人、湖南籍1人、四川籍1人，车行人员6人、酒店工作人员2人、地方管理人员1人。
Nine people escaped by themselves, including five from Fujian, one from Anhui, one from Heilongjiang, one from Hunan, one from Sichuan, six from a garage, two from hotel staff and one from a local administrator.
